snippet.title: The Sims 3 Outdoor Living Stuff Launch Trailer
snippet.description: Give the ultimate in luxury outdoor living for your Sims with The Sims™ 3 Outdoor Living Stuff! Whether they're decorating the perfect patio, setting the mood with a new hot tub, or firing up a state-of-the-art grill for the ultimate BBQ, your Sims' outdoor decor is getting a boost.
